	<div id="display_answer">
		<input type="button" name="answer" value="Answer" onclick="show_ans()" />

		<div id="welcomeDiv"  style="display:none;" class="answer_list" > 
			<p>It is a trick question, it is not possible. Since the car has already travelled 60 km at 30 km per hour, there is only 60km left which is not enough distance to get the average speed up to 60km per hour.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
